{"tid":2149130,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有數學題想問問","createTime":"2020-08-10T08:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T10:06:43.000Z","uid":25901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f15687d61993c2cfe87321ffe376d0c3f90f8d9a","tid":2149130,"uid":25901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:51:40.000Z","msg":"假設小明第一個月投資10,000在股票A上<br />\n然後每個月再投資5000在股票A上<br />\n假設股票每個月回報利潤都有5%<br />\n一年後連本金總共有幾多錢？<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩公式可以計算以上題目？<br />\n第一個月：10,000(1+5%)=10,500<br />\n第二個月：[5000+10,000(1+5%)](1+5%)=16275<br />\n第三個月：{5000+[5000+10,000(1+5%)]}(1+5%)=<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第n個月既同r%既月回報公式係咪應該係：<br />\n5000(1+5%)^(n-2)+5000(1+r%)^(n-1)+10000(1+r%)^n<br />\n<br />\n第十二個月換言之即係<br />\n5000(1+5%)^(12-2)+5000(1+5%)^(12-1)+10000(1+5%)^12?"},{"pid":"f309ec322c9fa682afaff7e7c146f106c0964ea6","tid":2149130,"uid":25901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T09:03:24.000Z","msg":"上面打錯左<br />\n<br />\n第n個月既同r%既月回報公式係咪應該係：<br />\n............+5000(1+r%)^(n-3)+5000(1+5%)^(n-2)+5000(1+r%)^(n-1)+10000(1+r%)^n<br />\n<br />\n第十二個月換言之即係<br />\n5000(1+5%)^(12-11)...............+5000(1+5%)^(12-2)+5000(1+5%)^(12-1)+10000(1+5%)^12?"},{"pid":"831800e370c66c66fc085896ee1b975ac0643a2b","tid":2149130,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f309ec322c9fa682afaff7e7c146f106c0964ea6","tid":2149130,"uid":25901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T09:03:24.000Z","msg":"上面打錯左<br />\n<br />\n第n個月既同r%既月回報公式係咪應該係：<br />\n............+5000(1+r%)^(n-3)+5000(1+5%)^(n-2)+5000(1+r%)^(n-1)+10000(1+r%)^n<br />\n<br />\n第十二個月換言之即係<br />\n5000(1+5%)^(12-11)...............+5000(1+5%)^(12-2)+5000(1+5%)^(12-1)+10000(1+5%)^12?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T09:09:39.000Z","msg":"仲有一個5000（1+5%）^（12-12）"},{"pid":"1fc048cf5b1d7e93811b2b65287019bc74d9a658","tid":2149130,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T09:24:38.000Z","msg":"既然你拆咗出嚟, <br />\n咁你咪s